ublic broadcast television channel, took sixth place with its \\\"Superhumans\\\" trailer for the Rio Paralympics 2016.\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Channel\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5457}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5482}, {\"ngram\": \"public broadcast television\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5510}, {\"ngram\": \"sixth place\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5536}, {\"ngram\": \"its \\\"Superhumans\\\" trailer\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 3-minute video ad got a score of 55.7%.\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 3-minute video ad\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5619}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5631}, {\"ngram\": \"55.7%\", \"from\": 5635, \"to\": 5640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your Goodness is Your Greatness from P&G took seventh place, with 55.5% of viewers responding with intense positive emotions.\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5682, \"end\": 5685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"P&G\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your Goodness\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5658}, {\"ngram\": \"Your Greatness\", \"from\": 5662, \"to\": 5676}, {\"ngram\": \"seventh place\", \"from\": 5691, \"to\": 5704}, {\"ngram\": \"55.5%\", \"from\": 5711, \"to\": 5716}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5727}, {\"ngram\": \"intense positive emotions\", \"from\": 5744, \"to\": 5769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"P&G was founded in 1837 by William Procter and James Gamble.\", \"from\": 5776, \"to\": 5836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5776, \"end\": 5779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"P&G\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http: